doc.after: Timberlake included "Cabaret" on the set list of his 2013-14 worldwide tour entitled The 20/20 Experience World Tour.[25] In a review of the concert that took place at the United Center in Chicago on February 16, Claudia Perry of the Chicago Tribune wrote "the whole apparatus returned to the A position (hey, Timberlake likes golf) while he performed 'Cabaret' and 'Take Back the Night'."[26]
